I"K<p>When considering <a class="internal-link" href="/secondbrain/conversational-interfaces-render-knowledge-bases-into-agents">extractive question answering systems</a> based on <a class="internal-link" href="/secondbrain/written-word-is-a-proxy-for-thought">text</a>, two subtasks can be identified: extracting information from text in advance and relaying user queries to that information. This decoupling makes <a class="internal-link" href="/secondbrain/guided-search-in-attention-is-multi-pass-filtering-in-machine-learning">question answering more accessible and efficient</a>.</p>
